OL,3,CExtreme rain leaves farmers with dead
OL,4,Clambs and decimated crops
OL,6,FSouth west England saw the wettest
OL,7,FFebruary on record earlier this year
OL,8,Fand across the country, there was 29%
OL,9,Fmore rainfall than the average, ITV
OL,10,FNews' Sangita Lal reports
OL,12,FCrouched down in a biscuit wheat
OL,13,Ffield, Tom Collins - a Wiltshire
OL,14,Farable - rolls soil between his hands
OL,15,Fand shows me a lump of mud, which he
OL,16,Fsays means it's too wet for any of his
OL,17,Fcrops to grow.
