OL,4,Clambs and decimated crops
OL,6,FThis year's storm season also brought
OL,7,Fthe most named storms since 2015 and
OL,8,Feven though the extreme conditions
OL,9,Fhave become calmer, farmers crops are
OL,10,Fstill being decimated by the effects.
OL,12,FMr Collins - whose family have farmed
OL,13,Fon the same land for more than a
OL,14,Fhundred years - says he has now given
OL,15,Fup trying to grow crops on some of his
OL,16,Ffields for the first time
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/9
