OL,3,CExtreme rain leaves farmers with dead
OL,4,Clambs and decimated crops
OL,6,F"In the Autumn we were pulling seeds
OL,7,Fout of the ground and they had just
OL,8,Fgone to mush because they had just
OL,9,Frotted away in the ground," Mr Collins
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"It probably cost us around #100,000
OL,13,Fin lost income."
OL,15,FIt's not just vulnerable crops that
OL,16,Fcan't cope, lambs are struggling to
OL,17,Fsurvive the wet weather too.
