OL,4,Clambs and decimated crops
OL,6,FThe government is now to support
OL,7,Ffarmers who've suffered uninsurable
OL,8,Fdamage from severe flooding.
OL,10,FGrants between #500 and #25,000 will
OL,11,Fbe given to those who are eligible,
OL,12,Fbut it is not being offered across the
OL,13,Fcountry.
OL,15,FCurrently, grants are only available
OL,16,Fwhere the Flood Recovery Framework has
OL,17,Falready been activated to help farms
OL,18,Fthat the government says have
OL,19,Fexperienced the highest levels of
OL,20,Fflooding.
