OL,3,CExtreme rain leaves farmers with dead
OL,4,Clambs and decimated crops
OL,6,FThese are Gloucestershire,
OL,7,FLeicestershire, Lincolnshire,
OL,8,FNottinghamshire, Somerset,
OL,9,FWarwickshire, West Northamptonshire,
OL,10,FWiltshire and Worcestershire.
OL,12,FBut there are criticisms about the
OL,13,Fscheme as it's not available across
OL,14,Fthe country and for those who are
OL,15,Feligible, they say not enough money is
OL,16,Fbeing given and farmers won't receive
OL,17,Fit in time for it to help.
OL,19,FTom Collins told ITV News that
OL,20,Fgovernment grants have come 'too late'
OL,21,Fand 'financially aren't enough'
